    "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><big><big><big>Bateau-feu</big></big></big>\n</p><p>Une structure en forme de navire utilisée à la place d’une bouée lumineuse dans les eaux où il existe de forts courants, ou lorsqu’une élévation plus grande que celle d’une bouée lumineuse est nécessaire. \n</p><p><br>\nLa source: <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"600a74804a1e9a2e1e2fbcc0523a3b4b\">IHO</span> Dictionary – <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"5dbc98dcc983a70728bd082d1a47546e\">S</span>-32, fourni par le comité <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"47f45e65244c17ec9fa8771a5c6d60e1\">ARM</span> dans un document ARM7-12.1.7 en 2017.\n</p><p><br>\n</p><p><br>\n<i>Cette définition remplace la définition numéro 8-2-020 dans l'édition originale du dictionnaire <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> (1970-1989).</i>\n</p><p><br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Light_float_(2)\" title=\"Light float (2)\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n • <span lang=\"fr\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">français</a></span>\n • <span lang=\"es\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/Light_float_(2)/es\" title=\"Light float (2)/es\">español</a></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"600a74804a1e9a2e1e2fbcc0523a3b4b\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Hydrographic Organization\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"5dbc98dcc983a70728bd082d1a47546e\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>South\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"47f45e65244c17ec9fa8771a5c6d60e1\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Aids to Navigation Requirements and Management Committee (IALA)\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615121358\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.034 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.040 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 76/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1095/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 275/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 3/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    9.428      1 Template:Languages\n100.00%    9.428      1 -total\n 61.00%    5.751      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:3032-0!canonical and timestamp 20260615121358 and revision id 8516. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n 